<h2>Try our Cinnamon Roast Coffee Beans!</h2>

<p id="cinnamon">
  Our Cinnamon roast coffee beans are not to be confused with cinnamon-flavoured
  coffee.
  <!--(Pavoni, 2021)-->
  The coffee beans have a light brown color due to being taken out of the
  roaster early in first crack.
  <!--(Pavoni, 2021)-->
  Because of its roasting process, it has a grassy and highly acidic taste when
  brewed.
  <!--(Pavoni, 2021)-->
</p>
